steps.html_instructions: Take exit 243 on the left for Mounds Blvd
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-35E S, follow signs for Interstate 35E S

I-35E S turns slightly right and becomes I-35 S
Entering Iowa
Take the I-35 S/I-80 exit toward Kansas City/Council Bluffs/Davenport
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-35 S/I-80 W/Kansas City/Council Bluffs and merge onto I-35 S/I-80 W

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-35 S
Entering Missouri
Take exit 12A to merge onto I-435 S toward St Louis
Take exit 71A for US-71 S toward I-470 E/US-50 E/Lee's Summit/Grandview
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for US 71 S/Joplin/Interstate 470 E/US 50 E/Lee's Summit
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for US-71 S/Grandview and merge onto I-49/US-71 S
Take exit 53 for Missouri 96/U.S. 71 Business/Missouri 171 N/Central Ave toward Missouri 571 S/Webb City
Take exit 20 on the left to merge onto I-40 E toward Alma/Little Rock
Keep right at the fork to continue on US-65 S, follow signs for Interstate 30 W/Little Rock
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
